      "step_type": "reasoning",
      "content": "## 1) STRUCTURE ANALYSIS (what\u2019s in the molecule)\n**SMILES:** `COC(=O)c1[nH]c2cc(F)ccc2c1[C@@H]1C[NH2+]CC[C@H]1F`",
